Output examples/runtime/multi_agent_workflow/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1500
Set Height 950
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 34
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Padding 18

Hide
Type "cd /Users/yasik/code/personal/agentlane" Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Type "UV_CACHE_DIR=/tmp/uv-cache uv run python examples/runtime/multi_agent_workflow/main.py" Sleep 250ms Enter
Sleep 5s
